title: 2010 European Cadet Judo Championships
text:
The 2010 <a href="European%20Cadet%20Judo%20Championships">European Cadet Judo Championships</a> is an edition of the <a href="European%20Cadet%20Judo%20Championships">European Cadet Judo Championships</a>, organised by the <a href="International%20Judo%20Federation">International Judo Federation</a>. It was held in <a href="Teplice">Teplice</a>, <a href="Czech%20Republic">Czech Republic</a> from 2 to 4 July 2010.
